thread.title: Dollar Slides Ahead of Key Data

author: Ira Iosebashvili
title: Dollar Slides Ahead of Key Data
text:
The dollar slid Tuesday, as some investors locked in profits on the U.S. currency a day ahead of key economic data.
The Wall Street Journal Dollar Index, which measures the U.S. currency against a basket of 16 others, was recently down 0.4% to 83.74.
Two weeks of market turbulence have pushed haven-seeking investors into the dollar, lifting...
